{{champion:103}} 

Whenever she is at a strong point(not even OP) she is obnoxious to play against because she literally does everything. She has the waveclear and safe harass of a mage, the slipperiness of an assassin, the burst damage of an assassin, deals true damage, has long range hard CC, gets free healing off her passive... there is actually no way to punish a good Ahri player with a counterpick either because they'll just safely farm by their turret till she becomes damn near ungankable because she's just that safe. 

The last time Ahri was strong she had a 24% playrate with a 54% winrate.

{{champion:10}} 
She either does everything you do but better or outright cockblocks whatever you were trying to do
Fuck Kayle,~~ bush-league super food~~

